title: Cal Smart Salmon and Zesty Slaw Tacos with Chipotle Sauce and Feta
description: Salmon gets a quick sear in the pan with our Enchilada Spice Blend for this easy and delicious weeknight number. The lime-garlic slaw is refreshingly light, while the chipotle drizzle gives these handhelds a welcome kick!

